Well @Ogre1983, your issue is different to @carbohydrates, I see you're using an AMD card, try starting KSP from the terminal with this command line argument, (cd to your KSP folder first).

./KSP.x86_64 -force-gfx-direct

This will force the Unity engine to use single threaded rendering.
